    "description": "HAELE 3D - Feet Poses Pro 是一个易于使用的解剖学绘画参考工具，适用于初学者到高级艺术家。通过多种可编辑的选项，它作为学习如何绘制人类脚的资源。不论您的艺术风格是写实的、风格化的、卡通的、动漫的，还是介于两者之间的，这款易于使用的应用程序补充了教程，并帮助您练习从草图到完成的脚部绘画技巧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/27a14c0181b9acc5cfbb0c9eba7267e3.poster.avif?t=1769519591\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/27a14c0181b9acc5cfbb0c9eba7267e3.webm?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/27a14c0181b9acc5cfbb0c9eba7267e3.mp4?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/90cc68a77dc9e7356ed2fbb02d75517a.poster.avif?t=1769519591\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/90cc68a77dc9e7356ed2fbb02d75517a.webm?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/90cc68a77dc9e7356ed2fbb02d75517a.mp4?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/824239d3211c5e6b99235b7ea8854fe4.poster.avif?t=1769519591\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/824239d3211c5e6b99235b7ea8854fe4.webm?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/824239d3211c5e6b99235b7ea8854fe4.mp4?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/5b0968eb0b3975e719dd2b1a8f938989.poster.avif?t=1769519591\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/5b0968eb0b3975e719dd2b1a8f938989.webm?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327780/extras/5b0968eb0b3975e719dd2b1a8f938989.mp4?t=1769519591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无论您的脚是褶皱的还是光滑的、纤细的还是多肉的、脏的还是干净的、湿的还是干的、有纹路的还是没有纹路的，HAELE 3D都能根据您的要求制作出一双完美的脚。<br><br>HAELE 3D - Feet Poser Pro 可渲染逼真和风格化的脚部绘图参考姿势和动画。可编辑脚底皱纹、指甲油、静脉、指纹甚至老茧等每个细节。许多内置预设、自定义背景、颜色、材质、灯光等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><br>- 50 多种预设姿势<br>- 50+ 种预设动画<br>- 30 个预设场景<br>- 自定义姿势<br>- 11 个变形目标：重量、光滑度、脚踝尺寸、脚掌宽度、脚跟宽度、平底、足弓、拇趾外翻、脚趾长度、第二脚趾长度、脚趾圆度、指甲长度 <br>- 可编辑的皮肤材质：皱纹、污垢、湿润、血管、细节、反射率、色调、饱和度、变化<br>- 颜色：预设皮肤颜色、灰度和肤色，完全可编辑的颜色区域<br>- 指甲：长度、光泽、色调、指甲油颜色<br>- 自定义图像背景<br>- 可编辑灯光 3 点灯光（颜色、强度转换）、环境灯光（HDRI 地图、强度）、地面灯光（颜色、强度） <br>- 环境 HDRI 工作室背景、各种环境、纯色、 <br>- 地板开关、颜色、反射率<br>- 可调整摄像机角度、位置、位置和视野<br>- 保存和加载场景<br>- 加载预设",
